name: .SZ File Extension
summary: Learn about .SZ files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Custom Winamp skin downloaded by Internet Explorer; used to modify the interface of Winamp, a popular music player for Windows.

content: NOTE: Internet Explorer changes the extension from .WSZ to ".sz" when the file is downloaded. The extension must be changed from ".sz" back to ".wsz" in order to work correctly.
